This is a java project to help extract localizable resource from source code.

Gradle build system is used in this project. Information about gradle can be
found in http://www.gradle.org.

To build this project, please follow this link
  http://www.gradle.org/docs/current/userguide/installation.html
to install Gradle. After that, use following simple commands to play with the code.

To build:
  gradle compileJava

To test:
  gradle test

To generate jar:
  gradle jar

If there is something wrong, try to do a :
  gradle clean

Further problems, please refer to Gradle's document for help. ;)


